children.key: Does the manager shall submit a list of federal aviation registration numbers twice yearly to the department in May and November of all aircraft based at his airport?

Does the manager shall display the local traffic pattern, airport traffic safety rules, any noise abatement procedures, and any special orders relating to the airport and its operations at a prominent location on the airport?
Has the manager shall file a notice to airmen with the Federal Aviation Administration designating any changes in airport conditions that may effect safety?
Is the  airport manager, or his authorized representative, shall be available during all hours of operation?

key: Is this airport manager performing all their duties?
